<plot>Madagascar is a wondrous land - full of mythical secrets, strange cultures and exotic nature. This documentary shows the stunning beauty and diversity of Madagascar's nature, the traditional and cultural relationship between the local people and their environment, and most of all it shows what the local people do to preserve their natural treasures.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?350552</url></doc>
